data.description: Welcome Home! This charming property boasts a farmhouse-inspired exterior, accentuated by beautiful landscaping and a quaint front porch. Step inside and discover the spacious dining room, setting the stage for the inherent charm within. The open-concept gourmet kitchen boasts quartz countertops, rich espresso cabinets, and stainless steel appliances, perfect for entertaining or cozy family nights. Retreat to the owner's suite with bay windows overlooking the backyard and a large bathroom with dual vanities, a tiled walk in shower and a nice sized walk in closet! The Davidson floorplan also offers three additional bedrooms and a second bathroom so there is room for everyone! Enjoy sitting on the covered lanai with a cup of coffee or glass of wine. The shed in the backyard provides additional storage. Nestled in desired Plummer Creek community with low HOA and NO CDD, this home offers convenience and comfort. Schedule your tour today!
